snippet.title: Maybe Sexy Amber Heard Is All About Love And Charity
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has settled up and ended a serious divorce battle filled with unproven accusations against Johnny Depp. Everyone thought it was about the money. But this may be a Robin Hood or Robin Heard story as it now appears she is taking from the Rich Depp and giving to the poor and needy. Let's see if that turns out to be true and in the meantime we will give her a cautious Kudo. In any event she sure is super hot sexy looking and a good actress as well.
